
form(method='post',name='trimPosts',action='/trimposts')
    legend Older Posts
    span.warn.js-warn
    input(type='hidden',name='urlList',value='[]')
    ol
        li
            | You have a lot of unread posts.  Would you rather forget about the older ones?
        li
            label(name='countToKeep') Choose how many posts to keep:
                input(name='countToKeep',type='number',value='24')
        li
            | Mark the remaining older posts as finished:
            input(name='submitTrimPosts',type='submit',value='Mark finished')  
        li
            | You will have to do this multiple times if the site is still discovering new posts.


    
